org.apache.pig.data

Class BinSedesTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.pig.data.AbstractTuple
      • org.apache.pig.data.DefaultTuple
        • org.apache.pig.data.BinSedesTuple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable, Tuple

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class BinSedesTuple
extends DefaultTuple
    This tuple has a faster (de)serialization mechanism. It to be used for storing intermediate data between Map and Reduce and between MR jobs. This is for internal pig use only. The serialization format can change, so do not use it for storing any persistant data (ie in load/store functions).
